# Bug 02: Navigation issues and intermittent 502 error in generators section

## Description
While interacting with generator navigation, some buttons do not switch pages correctly. In some cases, clicking different generators results in no change or triggers a 502 Bad Gateway error.

## Steps to reproduce
1. Open website
2. Navigate to “Functions” section
3. Click on different generators (e.g. Grid Generator → Favicon Generator → CSS Optimization)
4. Repeat switching between generators

## Actual result
- Some navigation clicks do not change the page
- In some cases, a 502 Bad Gateway error appears
- Behavior is inconsistent (works after refresh or random interactions)

## Expected result
Each generator button should reliably navigate to the correct page without errors.

## Environment
- Chrome (Desktop)
- Mobile browser (partial reproduction)

## Severity
High (intermittent functional + backend issue)
